<br>
That much being said, you guys will need some very solid strategy to get past the initial 5 mob pop without getting hit.  Perhaps you can position 4 of the mages at the 4 corners of the room where the outside mobs pop.  Two mages can be positioned in the center to kill the middle mob.<br>
<br>
Everybody pet tanks a mob, and nukes the main mob.  Have one mage choose the next target and all assist him.<br>
<br>
